dct_title_s: [Map of the country from Gulf of Venice - Belgrade - to Black Sea, the eastern sheet marked] MDLX [1560]
dct_description_sm: Shows the Gulf of Venice and the Adriatic coast from Venice to Croatia. Relief shown pictorially. Title and imprint from Tooley. Historic Maps copy imperfect: western sheet only.
